data.description: No need to look any more!! This is the one!! Single story with 1866 sq. ft. The kitchen has granite countertops with granite island. Eat-in kitchen area. Walking distance to Laurel Elementary School. Only 1 block to the Nutmeg Park. Just minutes to Highway 4 by-pass. This property has a dining room next to the family room with a fireplace. Exterior was painted in September 2023. The backyard has a cute play house. Concrete patio with small retaining wall. Many fruit trees. Low maintenance yards. Some personal items are still inside. The Washer, dryer, kitchen refrigerator all stay. Freezer in the garage stays with the house also.
